From: KernelPatch CI <ci@example.com>
Subject: [PATCH] fs/proc/base: include <linux/susfs_def.h> for SUSFS macros

SukiSU 的 SUSFS 补丁在 fs/proc/base.c 里调用了 SUSFS_IS_INODE_OPEN_REDIRECT
和 SUSFS_IS_INODE_SUS_MAP 宏，但没有 include 提供这些宏的 <linux/susfs_def.h>，
导致开启 CONFIG_KSU_SUSFS_OPEN_REDIRECT / CONFIG_KSU_SUSFS_SUS_MAP 时编译报：

  error: call to undeclared function 'SUSFS_IS_INODE_OPEN_REDIRECT'
  error: call to undeclared function 'SUSFS_IS_INODE_SUS_MAP'

在 cpufreq_times.h 之后追加条件 include，开关跟随 SUSFS 配置。
所有受影响的 OnePlus 机型 (sm8750/sm8850/...) 都需要这个修复。
---
 common/fs/proc/base.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/common/fs/proc/base.c b/common/fs/proc/base.c
--- a/common/fs/proc/base.c
+++ b/common/fs/proc/base.c
@@ -98,6 +98,10 @@
 #include <linux/resctrl.h>
 #include <linux/cn_proc.h>
 #include <linux/ksm.h>
 #include <linux/cpufreq_times.h>
+#if defined(CONFIG_KSU_SUSFS_SUS_MAP) || defined(CONFIG_KSU_SUSFS_OPEN_REDIRECT)
+#include <linux/susfs_def.h>
+#endif
+
 #include <trace/events/oom.h>
 #include <trace/hooks/sched.h>
 #include "internal.h"
